We plan to start delivery only soon and will launch this deliciousness as part of our re-opening soon as we are allowed to gather again! Pour your favorite beverage, turn on @dnice or the next @verzuztv battle and sink your teeth into our delicious food.  Stay tuned and follow our page @bentdidit for updates! We're taking this time to revamp and pivot like many small business owners but we are coming for you with the brand new flavor #losangeles ü§§ü§§! We miss y'all! Brand new menu debuts soon! It isn‚Äôt easy right now for companies in the business of food...like us. But yesterday we spent some time in the test kitchen with our budding young entrepreneur. When life gives you lemons, you make lemonade. No business and no school but we have to keep our minds occupied and what better way to keep hope alive than to explore new products that are timely with the current situation. So, we made organic body butters and hand sanitizer for Lou Lou‚Äôs Body Food and Sea Moss, Immunity Boosting Elderberry Syrup with vitamin C and zinc, and Turmeric Shots for B. Sting‚Äôs Body Line! Got some home economics and marketing lessons in while we were at it! Just waiting on our graphic artist, Tyson of TIP, LLC, to crank out our new branding!
